{"tid":2452431,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"2020 PSII 二級私人秘書ST/interview討論","createTime":"2021-03-18T23:45:02.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-22T09:12:24.000Z","uid":32234,"like":0,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"5d2c0f94ff8aa9c794511500fe76c455c5910b53","tid":2452431,"uid":32234,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-18T23:45:02.000Z","msg":"2020年二級私人秘書公開招聘計劃<br />\n<br />\n2020 年二級私人秘書公開招聘已於2020年12月24日截止申請。<br />\n <br />\n2020年公開招聘計劃時間表 註 1<br />\n<br />\n 事項<br />\n 時間<br />\n(1) 二級私人秘書職位申請日期 註 2<br />\n 2020年12月11日至2020年12月24日<br />\n(已截止)<br />\n(2) 技能測驗 註 3<br />\n(中文及英文文書處理速度測驗，以及一般商業電腦軟件應用知識測驗，包括Microsoft Office Word 2016及Excel 2016)\t<br />\n 2021年1月至2021年6月／7月<br />\n(3) 遴選面試 註 4及《基本法》知識測試 註 5<br />\n 2021年1月／2月至2021年8月<br />\n(4) 發出第一批聘書<br />\n 2021年3月／4月<br />\n(5) 發出遴選面試最後結果 註 6<br />\n 2021年12月"},{"pid":"e0d2fd8c1c38de33cb9328fb546e2c1e65dd1af2","tid":2452431,"uid":32234,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-18T23:45:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e86beaa715ef6a4d28637172d53166961b17dfa4","tid":2452431,"uid":196077,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-18T23:48:40.000Z","msg":"秘書係肉便器<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f3747c2571c6ed317bc3f741a08c88923fc31c63","tid":2452431,"uid":7255,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-19T00:42:10.000Z","msg":"留名<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1ed641f0faca7b645b6e05bdf04ab6dbcd116137","tid":2452431,"uid":20584,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-19T01:49:06.000Z","msg":"男仔係咪無機會<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/ass